This makes sense to me.
Other traceable decorators don't have such a high priority except the `TraceableValidator`. Here is the rationale: https://github.com/symfony/symfony/pull/22554#discussion_r116217802 (tl;dr: it's for extra safety, but as said above the result is surprising).
/cc @ogizanagi I think the same fix should apply to the `TraceableValidator`.

